QuestData.Title: Killing the Crawlers
QuestData.Description: Commander Skyshadow wants this tunnel cleared out so we can expedite trade with the Harborage. I must not leave my post here so I am leaving the task in your hands. Clear the tunnel and report to Commander Skyshadow at once!
QuestData.CompletionText: I swore I told Sentinel Moonwhisper to give direct orders. Are you not obeying them?
QuestData.RewardText: Good work, $c. That tunnel is our lifeline to the swamp.
